Your Majesty, permission to execute?

304
00:41:23,270 --> 00:41:26,360
Permission to execute?

305
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:28,740
Your Majesty, permission to execute?

306
00:41:29,110 --> 00:41:32,270
Permission to execute?

307
00:41:52,060 --> 00:41:55,090
He conspired
to assassinate Your Majesty

308
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,600
Show no mercy!

309
00:41:56,770 --> 00:42:00,360
This is the law of Qin!

310
00:42:03,270 --> 00:42:05,070
To conquer all under Heaven

311
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:07,370
The law must be enforced

312
00:42:07,540 --> 00:42:10,140
Set an example for the world!

313
00:42:12,110 --> 00:42:14,710
Execute him! Execute him!

314
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,280
Execute him!

315
00:42:19,590 --> 00:42:21,990
Execute him! Execute him!

316
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:23,680
Execute him!

317
00:42:33,270 --> 00:42:34,290
Execute him!

318
00:43:55,650 --> 00:43:59,550
Hail! Hail! Hail!

319
00:44:03,040 --> 00:44:06,800
Hail! Hail! Hail!

320
00:44:50,090 --> 00:44:53,370
Nameless was executed an assassin
but buried a hero...

321
00:44:53,390 --> 00:44:56,130
Sky gave up his sword
in honor of his fallen friends...

322
00:44:56,990 --> 00:45:00,490
In 221 B.C., the King of Qin
conquered all six kingdoms
and unified China.

323
00:45:00,510 --> 00:45:05,270
He ceased all expeditions
and built the Great Wall
to protect his subjects
from the Northern Tribes.

324
00:45:05,290 --> 00:45:08,590
The Qin Empire became the first
dynasty of China...

325
00:45:08,690 --> 00:45:11,590
And Qin Shihuang...
the First Emperor.

